title: Everything Comes Full Circle
description: A high school theatre group reunites nine years later to perform the same show that was a smashing hit. Despite all the time apart from each other, they fall into the same patterns that caused them so many problems in high school. Join the ensemble cast including Max, Luke, Lee, Maura, and more as they try to steal the show once again. Can they rekindle old flames, overcome personal doubts and feelings, and more importantly remember why they became actors in the first place? Find out what happens when Everything Comes Full Circle!
author: Jeff Trelewicz
